ENTITY_GENERAL_7.message: the {locality} branch office of SpaceCruise Inc

EQUIPMENT.message: You are not equipped to handle this mission. {unit} {equipment} required.

FLAVOUR_1_FAILUREMSG.message: Cha chreid mi nach do thill thu na bu tràithe! Abair caitheamh ùine!

FLAVOUR_1_HOWMUCHTIMETEXT.message: Feumaidh tu bhith air ais gu ruige {due} gus ath-phàigheadh slàn na coisgaise fhaighinn.

FLAVOUR_1_INTROTEXT.message: Tha stiùireadh trafaige aig {starport} feumach air do thaic SA BHAD gus cobhair a thoirt dha shoitheach-fànais dhen t-seòrsa {ship} a dh'fhulaing tubaist air {planet}. Chan eil fios againn an obraich na siostaman taice-beatha fhathast. Tha àrachas aig an t-soitheach le àrachas reul-phort {starport} agus còmhdachadh dhe {cash} aige airson ath-phàigheadh cobharach èiginnich.

FLAVOUR_1_LOCATIONTEXT.message: 'S e {planet} aig co-chomharran domhan-leud/domhan-fhad: {lat} / {long} a tha san t-ionad mu dheireadh aig an t-soitheach seo air a bheil tinn eòlach. 'S e {shiplabel} a th' ann an ID an t-soithich.

FLAVOUR_1_SUCCESSMSG.message: Mòran taing, seo faochadh mòr dhuinn! Cuiridh sinn an t-airgead thugad an ceartuair.

FLAVOUR_1_TYPEOFHELPTEXT.message: Chaidh aithris gu bheil sgioba dhe {crew} agus {pass} luchd-taisteil air bòrd an t-soithich. Tha sinn feumach air cuideigin a lorgas an soitheach 's a thogas an luchd-tarrsainn on làrach 's a bheir an-seo iad sa bhad.

FLAVOUR_2_ADTEXT.message: DH'FHALBH AN CONNADH AIR SOITHEACH air slighe {starport}.

FLAVOUR_2_FAILUREMSG.message: Cha chreid mi gun dug thu feitheamh orm cho fada sin thall an-seo! Chan fhaigh thu pàigheadh idir!

FLAVOUR_2_HOWMUCHTIMETEXT.message: Bu chòir dhut an connadh a lìbhrigeadh gu ruige {due} ach am faigh thu pàigheadh slàn.

FLAVOUR_2_INTROTEXT.message: Fhuair stiùireadh trafaige aig {starport} brath gun do dh'fhalbh an connadh air iteal a-steach {shiplabel} agus gun robh aca ri tìr a bhualadh gu h-èiginneach. Tha am paidhleat deònach {cash} a phàigheadh airson seirbheis connachaidh.

FLAVOUR_2_LOCATIONTEXT.message: Tha an soitheach a' feitheamh aig domhan-leud {lat} / domhan-fhad {long} air planaid {planet}.

FLAVOUR_2_SUCCESSMSG.message: Mòran mòran taing! Thug mi an duais shlàn dhut.

FLAVOUR_2_TRANSFERMSG.message: Chaidh {unit} tunna(ichean) de chonnadh a thar-chur.

FLAVOUR_2_TYPEOFHELPTEXT.message: Dh'iarr am paidhleat 1 tunna dhe chonnadh hàidhdreaidein.

FLAVOUR_3_ADTEXT.message: ÈIGINN MHEADAIGEACH air soitheach faisg air {starport}.

FLAVOUR_3_FAILUREMSG.message: 'S ann sgriosail a bha seo! Ùraichidh sinn na clàran agad mar as iomchaidh.

FLAVOUR_3_HOWMUCHTIMETEXT.message: Feumaidh am paidhleat ionaid an soitheach a ruigsinn gu ruige {due}.

FLAVOUR_3_INTROTEXT.message: Is mise {name} o stiùireadh trafaige aig {starport}. Tha mi ag iarraidh cobhair a thaobh èiginn mheadaigeach a' gabhail a-steach paidhleat iteil {shiplabel} air slighe {starport}.

FLAVOUR_3_LOCATIONTEXT.message: Bha aig soitheach ri tìr a bhualadh gu h-èiginneach air na co-chomharran seo: {lat} / {long}.

FLAVOUR_3_SUCCESSMSG.message: Mòran taing, a chomandair! Thug sinn aire air an taic a fhuair sinn uaibh.

FLAVOUR_3_TYPEOFHELPTEXT.message: Thoir paidhleat ionaid o {starport} dhan t-soitheach ach an toir e an soitheach air ais gu {starport}.

FLAVOUR_4_ADTEXT.message: DH'FHALBH AN CONNADH AIR SOITHEACH air {planet}.

FLAVOUR_4_FAILUREMSG.message: Cuiridh mi cuideigin eile. Na bodraig tuilleadh.

FLAVOUR_4_HOWMUCHTIMETEXT.message: For full pay the pilot expects you to deliver the fuel by {due}.

FLAVOUR_4_INTROTEXT.message: Bhruidhinn am paidhleat aig iteal {shiplabel} ri stiùireadh trafaige aig {starport}. Chan urrainn dhaibh gluasad ri linn tanca connaidh falaimh agus gheall iad {cash} a phàigheadh dha dhuine sam bith a bheir connadh dhan t-soitheach aca.

FLAVOUR_4_LOCATIONTEXT.message: The ship is stranded on {planet} at coordinates {lat} / {long}.

FLAVOUR_4_SUCCESSMSG.message: Very good. We will recommend you for future assignments.

FLAVOUR_4_TRANSFERMSG.message: Chaidh {unit} tunna(ichean) de chonnadh a thar-chur.

FLAVOUR_4_TYPEOFHELPTEXT.message: The pilot is asking for 1 ton of hydrogen fuel.

FLAVOUR_5_ADTEXT.message: DH'FHALBH AN CONNADH AIR SOITHEACH faisg air {starport}.

FLAVOUR_5_FAILUREMSG.message: People are just not dependable anymore.

FLAVOUR_5_INTROTEXT.message: {starport} air traffic control has identified a starship with ID {shiplabel} drifting without fuel close-by. We will pay {cash} to anyone who will refuel the ship so they can vacate {starport} vicinity.

FLAVOUR_5_LOCATIONTEXT.message: The target ship is currently drifting within {dist} km from here. You will have to track down the exact location yourself.

FLAVOUR_5_SUCCESSMSG.message: We will make record of your timely completion of the task.

FLAVOUR_5_TRANSFERMSG.message: Chaidh {unit} tunna(ichean) de chonnadh a thar-chur.

FLAVOUR_5_TYPEOFHELPTEXT.message: We request the delivery of 1 ton of hydrogen fuel to the ship.

FLAVOUR_6_FAILUREMSG.message: What a disaster! This is the death sentence to our poor colleagues!

FLAVOUR_6_HOWMUCHTIMETEXT.message: You have to be back by {due}.

FLAVOUR_6_INTROTEXT.message: My name is {name} of {entity}. We lost contact with our {ship} {shiplabel} following {problem}. We are willing to pay {cash} for immediate help.

FLAVOUR_6_LOCATIONTEXT.message: Last known position was the vicinity of {planet} in the {system} [{sectorx},{sectory},{sectorz}] system, {dist} ly away from here.

FLAVOUR_6_SUCCESSMSG.message: Thank you! You can't imagine how relieved we are.

FLAVOUR_6_TYPEOFHELPTEXT.message: I need someone willing to leave immediately and bring our colleagues back to {starport}, should they be alive. The ship had {crew} crew and {pass} passengers on board.

FLAVOUR_7_ADTEXT.message: IMMEDIATE CREW TRANSPORT to the {system} system requested.

FLAVOUR_7_FAILUREMSG.message: Thank you very much, but you are too late!

FLAVOUR_7_HOWMUCHTIMETEXT.message: The replacement crew has to reach the ship by {due}.

FLAVOUR_7_INTROTEXT.message: My name is {name} of {entity}. Our only ship, {ship} {shiplabel}, is drifting with one crew member left on board the ship after {problem}. I am willing to pay {cash} for immediate help.

FLAVOUR_7_LOCATIONTEXT.message: You will find the ship in the {system} [{sectorx},{sectory},{sectorz}] system, {dist} ly from here. It is being kept in orbit around {planet}.

FLAVOUR_7_SUCCESSMSG.message: Thank you! I have been authorized to transmit the full payment.

FLAVOUR_7_TRANSFERMSG.message: {unit} has transfered to the target ship.

FLAVOUR_7_TYPEOFHELPTEXT.message: We can't return the ship without minimal crew present. I am searching for someone willing to transport a replacement crew of {deliver_crew} to our starship immediately.
